  </div>
         <div class="figure-media-gallery-slide"><div class="figure-media-gallery-img"><img class="article-rotator-img lazyload" data-src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2021-07/NEWS_13093513F6DDCAA45663C7482DB3814B.JPG?La9RDTfnc7NdbHYXt_cbfXJGaPk.dmO7&itok=-TLrzcxo" alt data-caption="习近平22日乘火车前往拉萨市，实地察看拉林铁路沿线建设情况。（新华社）" src="https://www.zaobao.com/realtime/china/undefined" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><div class="tint"></div></div>
